{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-fill-in-the-blank-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-discuss-popular-trends-in-technology/task-14","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Vežba 14","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Ethical concerns</span> je kao etička pitanja koja nam postavljamo o tome šta je u redu, a šta nije. U svakodnevnom životu, razmišljamo o pravdi, poštenju i dobroti. U svetu programiranja, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ethical concerns</span> su etičke odluke i brige koje programeri imaju u vezi sa uticajem svog rada na ljude i društvo. Na primer, programeri moraju razmišljati o privatnosti korisnika, pravima i bezbednosti kada razvijaju aplikacije.</p>\n<p>Primjeri: <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Programmers need to consider ethical concerns in their work.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">When you have ethical concerns, you think about the impact of the content on users and society.</span></p>\n<p>Slušaj zvuk i dovrši rečenicu.</p>\n</section>","instructions":"","explanation":null,"challengeType":22,"helpCategory":"English","superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","block":"learn-how-to-discuss-popular-trends-in-technology","lang":"en-US","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-discuss-popular-trends-in-technology/task-14"},"fillInTheBlank":{"sentence":"<p>Wow, that's incredible! But what about BLANK BLANK?</p>","blanks":[{"answer":"ethical","feedback":"<p>Kada govorimo o nečemu što ima <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ethics</span>.</p>"},{"answer":"concerns","feedback":"<p>Pitanja koja mogu da te uznemire, posebno ako nisi siguran o njima i njihovim posledicama.</p>"}]},"inputType":null,"tests":[],"transcript":null,"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-roof.png","characters":[{"character":"Sophie","position":{"x":50,"y":0,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"4.2-1.mp3","startTime":